[[File:Metin Ataseven.jpg|thumb|Metin Ataseven]]'''Metin Ataseven''' (born 1972) is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] politician, representing the [[Moderate Party]] in the [[Swedish Riksdag]].<ref>Sveriges Riksdag. ''[http://www.riksdagen.se/sv/ledamoter-partier/Hitta-ledamot/Ledamoter/Ataseven-Metin-0135054091316/ Metin Ataseven]''</ref> Ataseven was substitute for [[Mikael Sandström]] (2010-2012) and for [[Ewa Björling]] (2012-2013). From 1 January 2013 to October 2014, he was an ordinary member.

